Citation.sTitle: Excess Enthalpy, Density, Viscosity, and Speed of Sound for the Mixture Tetrahydropyran + 1-Butanol at (283.15, 298.15 and, 313.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: Excess enthalpies, densities, speeds of sound and viscosities at the temperatures (283.15, 298.15, 313.15) K are reported for the binary mixture tetrahydropyran + 1-butanol. Excess molar volumes have been calculated from the densities. The deviations in both the speeds of sound and the absolute viscosities have also been estimated. All the properties have been fitted to Redlich-Kister equations.
